<Tabs defaultValue="preview" className="w-full relative">
  <TabsList>
    <TabsTrigger value="preview">Preview</TabsTrigger>
    <TabsTrigger value="codesnippet">Code</TabsTrigger>
  </TabsList>
  <TabsContent value="preview">
    <ComponentPreview basicPadding={true}  name="infinityScroll" category="carousel" />
  </TabsContent>
  <TabsContent value="codesnippet">
    <CodeWrapper>
      <CodePreview name="infinityScroll" category="carousel" />

Add the following animations to your `tailwind.config.js` file:

```ts
tailwind.config = {
  theme: {
    extend: {
      animation: {
        'infinite-scroll': 'infinite-scroll 25s linear infinite',
      },
      keyframes: {
        'infinite-scroll': {
          from: { transform: 'translateX(0)' },
          to: { transform: 'translateX(-100%)' },
        },
      },
    },
  },
}
```
